window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>What would life be like if we lived wihtout anxiety about our imperfections? Is it really possible to accept ourselves so fully? Tara Brach answers an emphatic \"yes\" in <i>The Wisdom of Self-Acceptance</i>. Join this clinical psychologist and Buddhist meditation teacher as she shows you how to free yourself from the grip of insecurities about being good enough.</p>"; 
